---
title: Tomato-Garlic Ragu with Spaghetti
description: Who doesn’t love a hearty ragu to kick off the fall season! We’ve upgraded this classic comfort food with a fragrant, garlic-tomato sauce. We’ve also added zucchini for color and chili flakes for an extra kick. It wouldn’t be complete without that sprinkle of Parmesan cheese!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/tomato-garlic-ragu-wildfire-w40-9adaf675.jpg
